  <TITLE>Ability to upload files for return requests</TITLE>
  <DESCRIPTION>It would be beneficial for the customer to have the ability to upload attachments such as photos, and attachments to a return request. Currently there is no ability to do so. If items get damaged in shipping it would be nice to be able to have these on the return request. Let's add a setting indicating whether file uploading is allowed for return requests (enabled by default) Let's store them in &quot;Download&quot; table (similar to product attributes with &quot;file upload&quot; type)</DESCRIPTION>
